OL,3,CBishop pleads with Trump to 'have
OL,4,Cmercy' on LGBTQ+ people and migrants
OL,6,FThe Right Reverend Mariann Budde
OL,7,Fpleads with President Donald Trump to
OL,8,Fbe kind towards communities in the
OL,9,FUnited States who might be scared
OL,10,Ffollowing his inauguration
OL,12,FA bishop in Washington DC pleaded with
OL,13,FPresident Donald Trump to have mercy
OL,14,Fon LGBTQ+ communities and migrants in
OL,15,Fa speech on Tuesday.
OL,17,FWith the newly-inaugurated president
OL,18,Fin attendance, the Right Reverend
OL,19,FMariann Budde gave a sermon focused on
OL,20,Fnational unity - while Trump appeared
OL,21,Funmoved by her words.
