OL,3,CBishop pleads with Trump to 'have
OL,4,Cmercy' on LGBTQ+ people and migrants
OL,6,FBudde said they gathered "to pray for
OL,7,Funity as a people and a nation - not
OL,8,Ffor agreement, political or otherwise
OL,9,F- but for the kind of unity that
OL,10,Ffosters community across diversity and
OL,11,Fdivision".
OL,13,FShe ended her sermon with a direct
OL,14,Fappeal to Trump, to have mercy on
OL,15,FLGBTQ+ people and undocumented migrant
OL,16,Fworkers: "You have felt the
OL,17,Fprovidential hand of a loving God. In
OL,18,Fthe name of our God, I ask you to have
OL,19,Fmercy on the people in our country who
OL,20,Fare scared now."
