OL,6,FThe sermon came the day after Trump
OL,7,Fwas inaugurated for the second time
OL,8,Fand after he had already enacted a
OL,9,Flist of executive orders - including
OL,10,Fcurtailing a series of protections
OL,11,Faround LGBTQ+ rights.
