OL,6,FTrump said that only two sexes - male
OL,7,Fand female - will be recognised going
OL,8,Fforward, with the same order requiring
OL,9,Fthe government to use the term "sex"
OL,10,Frather than "gender".
OL,12,FThe Biden administration had made
OL,13,Fefforts to broaden gender identity
OL,14,Fdesignations, including on passports,
OL,15,Fwhere US citizens have been able to
OL,16,Fselect "X" as their gender marker
OL,17,Fsince 2022, but that has now been
OL,18,Frevoked.
