OL,6,FMigrants were also targeted in Trump's
OL,7,Finaugural speech and subsequent
OL,8,Fexecutive orders.
OL,10,FThe new president declared a "national
OL,11,Femergency" at the Mexican border and
OL,12,Fimmediately ended the use of an app
OL,13,Fthat had allowed people to book
OL,14,Fappointments at legal crossing points
OL,15,Fbefore entering the United States,
OL,16,Famong other measures.
OL,18,FReverend Budde has criticised Trump
OL,19,Fbefore, rebuking his "racialised
OL,20,Frhetoric" and blaming him for inciting
OL,21,Fviolence on January 6, 2020.
